reviewText: This is a cheap homemade documentary. Don't waste your money.
Very nice and I enjoyed it as much as my son, arrived safe and quickly. Would recommend this to any Coldplay Fan!
We love Cold Play live and this DVD is as grand as a live concert.  It was good to learn more about the band members.
I would have never bought this c/d but it was rated 5 stars thus I thought it was good. I bought this for my wife as a christmas gift and it was a bust. I thought it was a concert c/d.
